Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:08.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}我又走了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:14.09,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}それが強さだった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:14.09,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}把這稱作堅強
